parameters:
\nc<Member 2>It's because we drank so much strong alcohol and medicine at
the year-end party...

\nc<Saki>But, for some reason, all the members were given a short
vacation.

\nc<Member 3>That's because if we didn't take a break, some of us might
have actually died.

\nc<Saki>(Senpai... you're late. You're usually here before everyone
else... I hope you're safe.)

\nc<Saki>(By the end of the year-end party, my memory was hazy and I
don't know what happened.)
\nc<Member 2>It's almost time for the morning meeting... Huh?

\nc<>Mary, wearing a collar, seems somewhat vacant. Her whole
body is limp, and she appears to have lost her willpower...

\nc<Executive Officer>Mary has shown us some splendid work up until now, but as of
today, she will be retiring, so everyone should celebrate.

\nc<Executive Officer>Ah, don't worry. It's not a forced dispatch when I say
retirement. Mary is just becoming my third wife, so everyone
can rest easy.

\nc<Member>Senpai Mary worked so hard... In the end, a succubus is
always a succubus?
\nc<>A despairing atmosphere flows through the office...
\nc<>Mary somehow lifts her face and looks at Saki but...

\nc<>When the executive officer presses on the injection mark on
her arm, her body starts to tremble violently.

\nc<Executive Officer>Mary-chan, hurry up and say your goodbyes so we can go home?
Your favorite medicine is waiting for you.
\nc<>Mary laughs brokenly as she bids farewell to everyone.

\nc<>Saki feels a strong sense of disgust looking at the face of
the executive officer who seems to be enjoying the scene.

\nc<Senpai>Everyone... take care. I think I managed to endure quite
long after all.

\nc<>Tears flow from lifeless eyes. A silent lament spreads among
the team members.

\nc<Senpai>...From now on, Saki will be the team leader. I've been very
grateful to all of you.

\nc<Member 3>We feel the same way, but if we don't keep our spirits up
here, we won't know what will happen to us either.

\nc<Saki>(To think Senpai is really leaving. How long can I
endure...)

\nc<Saki>(And what about these new succubi? What's going to happen to
us...?)
